data.description: Open the front french doors into the epitome of comfort, style, and elegance with this custom built home nestled in the historic town of Washington, LA. Located right in the heart of Hidden Village Subdivision, this home is a masterpiece of custom design. When you walk into the front door you will be greeted by the fresh and crisp updates. The home was recently painted with a serene white palette, creating an inviting and airy atmosphere. The open floor plan will welcome you with the kitchen that boasts updated white cabinets and a Chef's dream Wolf commercial range top, perfect for culinary adventures. Off from the kitchen you will enjoy the warmth of a gas fireplace complemented by built-in bookcases, creating the perfect setting for relaxation and entertainment. The split floor plan offers two guest bedrooms on one side with their own bathroom, and the other side of the home offers the main bedroom and bathroom. Off from ,the kitchen is a desk, half bath, laundry room and large pantry. The back door opens to a nice size covered patio and access to the covered carport. There is also an attached workshop ideal for hobbies or DIY projects. A generous .971-acre lot offers endless possibilities for outdoor activities and gardening. Also, spend time fishing in the neighborhood pond.  This pond covers almost 8 acres and is great for the fishing enthusiast. This home seamlessly blends modern amenities with timeless charm. Don't miss your chance to experience the enchantment of 337 Hidden Village Drive. Schedule a showing today.
